Republican%20president%20in%20his%20efforts%20to%20deport%20foreign%20pro-Palestinian%20students%20who%20are%20in%20the%20United%20States%20legally%20and%2C%20like%20Khalil%2C%20have%20not%20been%20charged%20with%20any%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%201952%20Immigration%20and%20Nationality%20Act%2C%20Trump-appointed%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20determined%20last%20month%20that%20Khalil%20could%20harm%20American%20foreign%20policy%20interests%20and%20should%20be%20deported%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Botherwise%20lawful%26quot%3B%20speech%20and%20activism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-alleges-palestinian-activist-mahmoud-khalil-covered-up-working-for-un-rights-body-7996159%5C%22%3EUS%20Alleges%20Mahmoud%20Khalil%20'Covered%20Up'%20Working%20For%20UN%20Rights%20Body%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComans%20said%20that%20she%20did%20not%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20overrule%20a%20secretary%20of%20state.%20The%20judge%20denied%20a%20motion%20by%20Khalil's%20lawyers%20to%20subpoena%20Rubio%20and%20question%20him%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20grounds%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20for%20his%20determination%20under%20the%201952%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge's%20decision%20came%20after%20a%20combative%2090-minute%20hearing%20held%20in%20a%20court%20located%20inside%20a%20jail%20complex%20for%20immigrants%20surrounded%20by%20double-fenced%20razor%20wire%20run%20by%20private%20government%20contractors%20in%20rural%20Louisiana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalil%2C%20a%20prominent%20figure%20in%20the%20pro-Palestinian%20student%20protest%20movement%20that%20has%20roiled%20Columbia's%20New%20York%20City%20campus%2C%20was%20born%20in%20a%20Palestinian%20refugee%20camp%20in%20Syria%2C%20holds%20Algerian%20citizenship%20and%20became%20a%20US%20lawful%20permanent%20resident%20last%20year.%20Khalil's%20wife%20is%20a%20US%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now