%20sent%20me%20to%20this%20court%2C%20a%20thousand%20miles%20away%20from%20my%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20her%20ruling%20turned%20on%20an%20undated%2C%20two-page%20letter%20signed%20by%20Rubio%20and%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20and%20to%20Khalil's%20counsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalil's%20lawyers%2C%20appearing%20via%20a%20video%20link%2C%20complained%20they%20were%20given%20less%20than%2048%20hours%20to%20review%20Rubio's%20letter%20and%20evidence%20submitted%20by%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20Comans%20this%20week.%20Marc%20Van%20Der%20Hout%2C%20Khalil's%20lead%20immigration%20attorney%2C%20repeatedly%20asked%20for%20the%20hearing%20to%20be%20delayed.%20Comans%20reprimanded%20him%20for%20what%20the%20judge%20said%20was%20straying%20from%20the%20hearing's%20purpose%2C%20twice%20saying%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Ban%20agenda.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComans%20said%20that%20the%201952%20immigration%20law%20gave%20the%20secretary%20of%20state%20%26quot%3Bunilateral%20judgment%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20his%20determination%20about%20Khalil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalil%20should%20be%20removed%2C%20Rubio%20wrote%2C%20for%20his%20role%20in%20%26quot%3Bantisemitic%20protests%20and%20disruptive%20activities%2C%20which%20fosters%20a%20hostile%20environment%20for%20Jewish%20students%20in%20the%20United%20States.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubio's%20letter%20did%20not%20accuse%20Khalil%20of%20breaking%20any%20laws%2C%20but%20said%20the%20State%20Department%20can%20revoke%20the%20legal%20status%20of%20immigrants%20who%20could%20harm%20US%20foreign%20policy%20interests%20even%20when%20their%20beliefs%2C%20associations%20or%20statements%20are%20%26quot%3Botherwise%20lawful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Comans%20ended%20the%20hearing%2C%20several%20of%20Khalil's%20supporters%20wept%20as%20they%20left%20the%20courtroom.%20Khalil%20stood%20and%20smiled%20at%20them%2C%20making%20a%20heart%20shape%20with%20his%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%