ng.%3Cp%3EHillary%20Grigonis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20can%20help%20you%20find%20your%20pet%20if%20they%20go%20missing%20by%20providing%20real-time%20information%20about%20their%20whereabouts.%20Using%20cellular%20data%20to%20connect%20with%20GPS%20satellites%2C%20these%20trackers%20can%20send%20your%20pet's%20location%20to%20your%20smartphone.%20Even%20more%2C%20some%20trackers%20allow%20you%20to%20set%20up%20a%20geofence%2C%20or%20virtual%20fence%2C%20around%20your%20home%2C%20and%20alert%20you%20if%20your%20dog%20exits%20the%20area.%20Many%20trackers%20also%20monitor%20your%20pet's%20activity%20level%2C%20from%20their%20daily%20steps%20to%20time%20at%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20there's%20a%20wide%20range%20in%20reliability%20and%20accuracy%20among%20different%20models%20%E2%80%94%20some%20trackers%20sound%20an%20alert%20within%20minutes%20of%20your%20dog%20stepping%20outside%20a%20virtual%20fence%20and%20others%20trackers%20may%20have%20you%20searching%20for%20your%20missing%20dog%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20the%20road.%20To%20find%20the%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%2C%20I%20tested%2010%20different%20options%20with%20my%20active%20springer%20spaniel.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop.tryfi.com%2Fproducts%2Fsmart-collar-v3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFi%20Series%203%3C%2Fa%3E%20delivered%20the%20best%20blend%20of%20features%2C%20but%20I%20also%20found%20options%20for%20comprehensive%20activity%20monitoring%20and%20the%20budget%20and%20privacy-conscious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20your%20dog%20wears%20a%20GPS%20tracker%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vetmed.wisc.edu%2Fpeople%2Fjessica-pritchard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jessica%20Pritchard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20clinical%20assistant%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Wisconsin-Madison%20School%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%2C%20says%20microchipping%20is%20still%20ess