%252F277143%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20at%20Chewy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20budget%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETractive%20GPS%20and%20Health%20Tracker%20for%20Dogs%204%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109047881xui-20%26h%3D6fc0b77eba78bcb1fe1ebbf3689b646ffb0e4ac51cf0279788ff31693406d28a%26postID%3D67f4190e3d37c2e3ad3cfaa5%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-gps-pet-trackers%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Ftractive-dog-gps-tracker-activity%252Fdp%252F290601%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20at%20Chewy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20privacy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECube%20GPS%20Tracker%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109047881xui-20%26h%3D2cea93c646e4a48a34ab965de5d921a4e5e08c68285d56a93b0bf92cdbab305a%26postID%3D67f4190e3d37c2e3ad3cfaa5%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-gps-pet-trackers%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fcube-real-time-gps-dog-cat-tracker%252Fdp%252F303999%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20at%20Chewy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b869e07e-2091-41d8-ae38-3791142a5fa5%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20overall%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20overall%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20durable%20design%20combined%20with%20consistent%2C%20accurate%20location%20tracking%20pushed%20the%20Fi%20Series%203%20to%20the%20top%20of%20our%20list%20for%20the%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers.%20While%20most%20trackers%20require%20you%20to%20attach%20them%20to%20your%20dog's%20existing%20collar%2C%20the%20Fi%20Series%203%20is%20a%20collar%20with%20a%20built-in%20durable%20metal%20tracker%2C%20available%20in%20four%20colors%20and%20five%20different%20sizes.%20The%20removable%20tracking%20device%20feels%20almost%20like%20a%20second%20buckle%2C%20a%20design%20that's%20both%20simple%20to%20use%20and%20comfortable%20for%20a%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collar%20consistently%20delivered%20quick%20and%20accurate%20location%20updates%20using%20a%20highly%20detailed%20map.%20Plus%2C%20it%20can%20do%20more%20than%20help%20find%20a%20lost%20dog.%20Its%20%26quot%3BSafe%20Zone%26quot%3B%20feature%20pings%20your%20smartphone%20if%20the%20tracker%20leaves%20a%20customizable%20geofence%20area%2C%20which%20helps%20prevent%20a%20wandering%20dog%20from%20getting%20too%20far%20from%20home.%20The%20Fi%20was%20consistently%20first%20among%20the%20trackers%20to%20alert%20me%20to%20a%20breached%20virtual%20fence%2C%20taking%20from%20one%20to%20five%20minutes.%20If%20you%20need%20to%20locate%20your%20dog%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20a%20built-in%20night%20light%20may%20help%2C%20but%20it%20isn't%20as%20bright%20as%20others%20I%20tested.%20I%20also%20wish%20it%20had%20a%20location%20calling%20feature%20(an%20audible%20sound%20alert)%20to%20help%20zero%20in%20on%20my%20dog's%20location%20when%20I%20couldn't%20see%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20photo%20of%20a%20springer%20spaniel%20wearing%20a%20blue%20collar%20with%20the%20Fi%20GPS%20tracker%20logo%20on%20it%20and%20a%20detailed%20satellite%20view%20of%20track%20lost%20dog%20in%20Fi%20app.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f9746ba466d2b74ab300b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fi%20Series%203%20came%20out%20on%20top%20in%20nearly%20all%20of%20our%20tests%20and%20offered%20precise%20location%20tracking.%3Cp%3EHillary%20Girgonis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20step%20count%20and%20sleep-tracking%20features%2C%20I%20could%20see%20how%20active%20my%20dog%20was.%20However%2C%20the%20Fi%20only%20tracks%20miles%20for%20walks%2C%20omitting%20steps%20around%20the%20house%20or%20yard%20from%20the%20tally.%20Ultimately%2C%20for%20activity%20tracking%2C%20I%20prefer%20the%20Whistle%20Go%20Explore%202%2C%20which%20counts%20distance%20and%20calories%2C%20a%20format%20I%20found%20easier%20to%20understand.%20Be%20aware%20that%20the%20Fi%20app%20is%20also%20packed%20with%20social%20features%20that%20are%20opt-out%20rather%20than%20opt-in%2C%20so%20be%20sure%20to%20check%20your%20settings%20if%20privacy%20is%20important%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20battery%20life%20was%20excellent.%20A%20magnetic%20charger%20is%20included%20and%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20base%20that%20connects%20to%20your%20WiFi%20to%20conserve%20battery%20life%20when%20your%20dog%20is%20within%20range.%20You%20can%20also%20switch%20to%20Bluetooth%20to%20conserve%20the%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collar%20is%20included%20in%20the%20subscription%2C%20which%20helps%20ease%20the%20higher%20subscription%20rate.%20As%20long%20as%20you%20have%20an%20active%20subscription%2C%20your%20collar%20is%20covered%20by%20a%20lifetime%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22baaaaac9-0164-4d71-95e4-ab55e71a1616%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20activity%20tracker%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20activity%20tracker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20three%20of%20our%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20monitor%20activity%2C%20the%20Whistle%20Go%20Explore%202%20collects%20the%20most%20helpful%20statistics%20in%20an%20easy-to-use%20app.%20The%20Whistle's%20distance%2C%20calorie%2C%20and%20active%20minute%20tracking%20was%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20understand%20than%20trackers%20that%20only%20counted%20steps.%20And%20it%20uses%20all%20this%20data%20to%20create%20a%20timeline%20of%20a%20dog's%20day.%20With%20it%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20see%20my%20dog's%20activity%20for%20each%20day%20and%20pinpoint%20trends%2C%20like%20how%20weather%20affected%20his%20activity%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPritchard%20says%20many%20owners%20assume%20that%20their%20dogs%20are%20playing%20while%20they%20are%20at%20work%2C%20but%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20pup%20is%20napping%20on%20the%20couch.%20Activity%20monitoring%20can%20provide%20both%20insight%20and%20added%20motivation%20to%20encourage%20activity%20in%20overweight%20pets%2C%20she%20says.%20However%2C%20while%20Whistle's%20list%20of%20activity-monitoring%20features%20is%20long%2C%20we%20caution%20against%20relying%20on%20its%20scratching%20and%20licking%20monitor%20and%20AI-powered%20Poop%20Scan%20for%20digestive%20health.%20These%20types%20of%20features%20are%20too%20new%20to%20have%20been%20tested%20for%20effectiveness%2C%20and%20observing%20your%20dog%20is%20often%20sufficient%20to%20spot%20potential%20skin%20issues%20associated%20with%20licking%20and%20scratching%2C%20Pritchard%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20image%20of%20a%20springer%20spaniel%20wearing%20a%20light%20blue%20collar%20with%20a%20gray%20Whistle%20GPS%20tracker%20attached%20and%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20app's%20activity%20tracking%20goals.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f974b13fe8d3928362e7de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Whistle%20Go%20Explore%202.0%20Smart%20Tracker%20provides%20a%20detailed%20history%20of%20your%20daily%20dog's%20activities.%3Cp%3EHillary%20Grigonis%3B%20Chewy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Whistle%20Go%20Explore%202%20also%20accurately%20pinpoints%20the%20location%20of%20a%20lost%20pet%20with%20a%20detailed%20map%20view.%20It%20provides%20geofence%20alerts%2C%20though%20they%20aren't%20as%20fast%20as%20the%20Fi%20Series%203.%20The%20Whistle%20alerts%20arrived%20in%20around%20eight%20minutes%20whereas%20the%20Fi%20sent%20alerts%20within%20five%20minutes%20or%20less.%20A%20bright%20light%20on%20the%20tracker%20can%20help%20you%20find%20your%20dog%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20but%20it%20lacks%20a%20location-calling%20sound%20that%20could%20be%20helpful%20when%20your%20dog%20is%20out%20of%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20waterproof%20tracker%20survived%20submersion%20and%20only%20showed%20minor%20damage%20from%20scratching.%20Despite%20being%20one%20of%20the%20smaller%20trackers%20I%20tested%2C%20it's%20rated%20for%20dogs%20over%2025%20pounds.%20You%20can%20place%20it%20on%20a%20smaller%20collar%20with%20the%20included%20snap%20attachment%20or%20on%20a%20larger%20collar%20with%20the%20provided%20hook-and-loop%20velcro%20attachment.%20Check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-collar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20collars%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20options%20in%20a%20range%20of%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aa818653-c2d9-4e2e-8886-d3f50ee1f365%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20tested%20the%202024%20Tractive%20model%2C%20and%20it's%20still%20available%20for%20purchase.%20Tractive%20has%20since%20released%20a%20new%20model%20that%20includes%20bark%20monitoring%20and%20offers%20a%20longer%20battery%20life%20(14%20days).%20We%20are%20testing%20it%20for%20an%20update%20to%20this%20guide%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGPS%20tracker%20subscription%20costs%20can%20add%20up%20quickly%2C%20but%20the%20Tractive%20GPS%20and%20Health%20Tracker%20for%20Dogs%20is%20the%20most%20affordable%20tracker%20with%20its%20device%20and%20subscription%20costs%20combined.%20Tractive%20offers%20accurate%20location%20tracking%20on%20an%20exceptionally%20detailed%20map%20that%20includes%20elevation%20and%20even%20how%20fast%20your%20pet%20is%20traveling.%20During%20my%20testing%2C%20I%20didn't%20encounter%20connectivity%20issues%20with%20any%20of%20the%20trackers%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20noting%20that%20Tractive%20is%20our%20only%20pick%20supported%20by%20three%20providers%3A%20AT%26amp%3BT%2C%20Verizon%2C%20and%20T-Mobile.%20It%20will%20connect%20with%20whichever%20service%20has%20the%20strongest%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tractive%20app%20was%20organized%20and%20intuitive%20and%20led%20me%20right%20to%20the%20tracker's%20location.%20It%20not%20only%20showed%20the%20location%20on%20a%20detailed%20map%20but%20also%20showed%20how%20far%20away%20I%20was%20from%20it.%20A%20ringtone%20emitted%20from%20the%20tracker%20also%20helped%20me%20find%20my%20dog%20when%20he%20was%20out%20of%20view.%20Within%20the%20app%2C%20I%20could%20see%20my%20dog's%20active%20minutes%20and%20calories%20burned%2C%20with%20a%20heat%20map%20displaying%20his%20favorite%20hangout%20spots.%20The%20app%20includes%20a%20leaderboard%20feature%20that%20shows%20local%20logs%20and%20their%20activity%20level.%20You%20also%20send%20friend%20requests%20to%20other%20users.%20You'll%20need%20to%20exit%20each%20leaderboard%20to%20opt%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20image%20of%20a%20springer%20spaniel%20wearing%20a%20light%20blue%20collar%20wth%20the%20white%20Tractive%20GPS%20devise%20attached%20and%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20map%20view%20of%20the%20lost%20dog%20tracker.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f974e93fe8d3928362e7ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlthough%20the%20Tractive%20GPS%20and%20Health%20Tracker%20for%20Dogs%20is%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20many%20devices%2C%20it%20is%20a%20highly%20reliable%20tracker.%3Cp%3EHillary%20Grigonis%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETractive%20packs%20a%20long%20list%20of%20features%20in%20a%20small%2C%20affordable%20tracker.%20However%2C%20the%20geofence%20notifications%20were%20slow.%20While%20no%20tracker%20offers%20instant%20alerts%2C%20the%20Tractive's%20typical%2015-minute%20alert%20time%20was%20longer%20than%20our%20top%20picks%20from%20Fi%20and%20Whisle%20%E2%80%94%20both%20are%20better%20options%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20the%20best%20geofence%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tractive%20device%20is%20relatively%20small%20and%20recommended%20for%20dogs%20weighing%20at%20least%208.8%20pounds.%20Its%20stretchy%20silicone%20bands%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20attach%20to%20most%20standard%20collars%20or%20even%20a%20harness.%20Although%20it's%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20it%20survived%20submersion%20in%20water%20and%20drops%2C%20only%20experiencing%20minor%20scratches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221152c440-1fb1-4e58-8ddd-a4b255d63371%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20privacy%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20privacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20GPS%20tracking%20device%20carries%20some%20level%20of%20privacy%20risk%2C%20but%20the%20absence%20of%20social-sharing%20app%20features%20creates%20fewer%20areas%20for%20potential%20vulnerabilities.%20With%20its%20simple%20app%2C%20the%20Cube%20GPS%20Tracker%20locates%20your%20dog%20%E2%80%94%20and%20nothing%20more.%20In%20fact%2C%20it's%20advertised%20not%20only%20for%20tracking%20pets%20but%20also%20for%20belongings%20like%20luggage%20and%20keys.%20To%20use%20it%20for%20your%20dog%2C%20will%20need%20to%20purchase%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109047881xui-20%26h%3Dab48762ca76ea2076ab3d2e403a36e5c149f5ca9aa42e248a71fd7baaf831f59%26postID%3D67f4190e3d37c2e3ad3cfaa5%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-gps-pet-trackers%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chewy.com%252Fcube-gps-dog-cat-collar-clips-3-count%252Fdp%252F304001%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20set%20of%20collar%20clips%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20sold%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cube%20GPS%20Tracker%20app%20accurately%20represented%20the%20tracker's%20location%2C%20providing%20driving%20directions%2C%20an%20optional%20satellite%20view%2C%20and%20location%20history.%20A%20location%20calling%20feature%20helped%20me%20pinpoint%20its%20location%20with%20a%20loud%20tone%20but%20there's%20no%20light%20for%20nighttime%20use.%20While%20there%20is%20an%20option%20to%20set%20up%20a%20virtual%20fence%2C%20I%20found%20the%20alerts%20arrived%20in%20between%203%20and%2015%20minutes%2C%20making%20it%20far%20less%20reliable%20than%20the%20Fi%20and%20Whistle%20trackers.%20The%20geofence%20is%20also%20less%20customizable%20and%20is%20limited%20to%20a%20circular%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20image%20of%20a%20springer%20spaniel%20wearing%20a%20light%20blue%20collar%20with%20the%20Cube%20GPS%20tracker%20attached%20and%20a%20smartphone%20with%20the%20location%20history%20portion%20of%20the%20Cube%20app%20displayed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f981afa466d2b74ab303f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20privacy%20is%20a%20priority%2C%20the%20Cube%20GPS%20tracker%20is%20an%20excellent%20choice%20for%20tracking%20a%20lost%20dog.%3Cp%3EHillary%20Grignonis%3B%20Chewy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cube%20GPS%20Tracker%20is%20one%20of%20the%20bulkier%2C%20heavier%20trackers%20and%20is%20best%20taken%20off%20at%20night%20for%20your%20pet's%20comfort.%20Attaching%20it%20to%20my%20dog's%20collar%20came%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20learning%20curve%20%E2%80%94%20the%20clips%20did%20not%20come%20with%20instructions%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn79eKVNPAIQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20make%20it%20obvious%20that%20you%20have%20to%20insert%20the%20bottom%20piece%20first%20for%20everything%20to%20lock%20into%20place.%20Subscription%20costs%20also%20sit%20on%20the%20higher%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22690af674-746c-444e-b441-27c6517fa9f2%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20GPS%20tracker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20have%20their%20limitations.%20These%20devices%20use%20cellular%20data%20to%20connect%20to%20GPS%20satellites%2C%20and%20then%20send%20the%20location%20data%20to%20the%20owner's%20tracking%20app.%20Like%20cellphones%2C%20GPS%20trackers%20won't%20work%20if%20there%20isn't%20a%20signal%2C%20like%20in%20some%20rural%20areas.%20Similarly%2C%20they%20work%20best%20with%20an%20unobstructed%20view%20of%20the%20sky%2C%20and%20accuracy%20can%20be%20decreased%20when%20tall%20buildings%20and%20other%20objects%20block%20the%20signal.%20Because%20of%20the%20potential%20of%20losing%20a%20pet%20in%20an%20area%20without%20a%20GPS%20signal%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20collar%20falling%20off%2C%20Pritchard%20says%20trackers%20should%20be%20used%20in%20addition%20to%20microchipping%2C%20rather%20than%20instead%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20trackers%20have%20a%20longer%20list%20of%20features%20than%20others%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20always%20mean%20they're%20the%20best%20choice.%20For%20example%2C%20Pritchard%20says%20features%20like%20monitoring%20for%20scratching%20and%20licking%20are%20too%20new%20to%20have%20been%20tested%20for%20their%20effectiveness.%20Below%20are%20the%20features%20we%20found%20most%20useful%20in%20our%20tests.%20With%20each%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20understand%20the%20technology's%20limitations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConnectivity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EConnectivity%20is%20key%20to%20finding%20a%20lost%20pet.%20GPS%20trackers%20connect%20to%20a%20cellular%20network%2C%20such%20as%20Verizon%2C%20AT%26amp%3BT%2C%20and%20T-Mobile.%20This%20allows%20you%20to%20find%20a%20missing%20pet%20as%20long%20as%20the%20dog%20hasn't%20wandered%20into%20an%20area%20that%20lacks%20cell%20coverage%20from%20the%20carrier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20purchase%20a%20collar%20that%20uses%20the%20same%20cellular%20network%20as%20your%20smartphone%2C%20if%20you%20live%20in%20an%20area%20where%20one%20network%20has%20limited%20connectivity%2C%20you%20will%20likely%20want%20to%20avoid%20trackers%20using%20that%20network.%20Trackers%20will%20also%20lose%20signal%20in%20the%20same%20places%20that%20your%20cellphone%20drops%20a%20call%2C%20like%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20a%20parking%20garage%20or%20a%20rural%20area%20too%20far%20from%20a%20cell%20tower.%20In%20this%20instance%2C%20many%20GPS%20trackers%20will%20show%20the%20last%20known%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20trackers%20also%20have%20WiFi%20and%20Bluetooth%20connectivity%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20monitor%20your%20pet%20while%20conserving%20battery%20life.%20Bluetooth%20can%20also%20be%20helpful%20when%20used%20along%20with%20cell%20coverage%20for%20pinpointing%20an%20exact%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20trackers%2C%20like%20Tile%20and%20Airtag%2C%20use%20Bluetooth%20exclusively.%20Bluetooth-only%20trackers%20need%20to%20be%20within%20100%20feet%20of%20a%20smartphone%20to%20work.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20we%20don't%20recommend%20trackers%20like%20Tile%20or%20AirTag%20for%20pets.%20While%20they%20can%20be%20great%20for%20finding%20your%20misplaced%20keys%20or%20backpack%2C%20the%20limited%20range%20isn't%20ideal%20for%20tracking%20a%20lost%20animal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGeofencing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20setting%20up%20a%20virtual%20boundary%2C%20trackers%20with%20geofencing%20will%20alert%20you%20if%20your%20pet%20leaves%20the%20area.%20That%20means%20you%20can%20get%20a%20ping%20to%20your%20phone%20when%20your%20dog%20leaves%20the%20yard%2C%20and%20then%20use%20the%20app%20to%20see%20where%20your%20dog%20is.%20The%20biggest%20thing%20to%20understand%20is%20that%20geofence%20alerts%20are%20not%20instantaneous.%20The%20tracker%20only%20sends%20a%20signal%20out%20every%20few%20minutes%2C%20otherwise%20the%20battery%20would%20only%20last%20a%20few%20hours.%20The%20geofence%20alerts%20typically%20took%20between%202%20and%2010%20minutes%20with%20our%20top%20picks.%20Just%20like%20you%20shouldn't%20skip%20microchipping%20because%20you%20have%20a%20GPS%20collar%2C%20dog%20owners%20should%20not%20skip%20training%2C%20leashes%2C%20or%20fences%20to%20rely%20exclusively%20on%20geofencing%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20not%20all%20geofences%20are%20equal.%20Some%20only%20allow%20you%20to%20create%20a%20circular-shaped%20geofence%2C%20while%20others%20allow%20you%20to%20create%20a%20custom%20shape%20that%20matches%20your%20yard.%20Other%20trackers%20require%20the%20geofence%20to%20be%20at%20least%20an%20acre%2C%20so%20those%20with%20small%20yards%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20match%20the%20geofence%20to%20their%20property%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EActivity%20tracking%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMany%20GPS%20trackers%20monitor%20a%20pet's%20activity%20levels%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20from%20how%20many%20steps%20they%20take%20to%20how%20often%20they%20are%20at%20rest.%20Pritchard%20says%20this%20feature%20can%20be%20helpful%20for%20pets%20that%20need%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20particularly%20for%20portions%20of%20the%20day%20when%20the%20owner%20is%20not%20home.%20She%20says%20many%20people%20expect%20their%20dogs%20are%20playing%20while%20they%20are%20at%20work%20when%20in%20reality%20they%20are%20often%20sleeping.%20Activity%20monitoring%20can%20be%20an%20added%20motivation%20to%20help%20get%20a%20pet%20moving.%20Sleep%20tracking%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20fairly%20new%20feature%20for%20collars%2C%20which%20means%20there%20haven't%20been%20many%20clinical%20trials%20demonstrating%20the%20effectiveness%20or%20accuracy%20of%20the%20feature%2C%20Pritchard%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrivacy%20and%20social%20features%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMuch%20in%20the%20same%20way%20humans%20can%20start%20a%20friendly%20Fitbit%20competition%2C%20some%20activity%20trackers%20for%20pets%20also%20integrate%20social%20features.%20For%20example%2C%20you%20can%20see%20which%20of%20your%20friends'%20pets%20had%20the%20most%20active%20day%20or%20connect%20with%20other%20pet%20owners%20nearby.%20While%20some%20people%20enjoy%20the%20social%20aspect%2C%20those%20concerned%20about%20privacy%20should%20buy%20a%20tracker%20that%20doesn't%20have%20a%20social%20component.%20%26quot%3BAny%20kind%20of%20social%20app%20is%20creating%20much%20higher%20inherent%20privacy%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fepic.org%2Fpeople%2Fjake-wiener%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJake%20Wiener%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20legal%20counsel%20at%20the%20Electronic%20Privacy%20Information%20Center%20and%20owner%20of%20a%20hound%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%20and%20waterproofing%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Water%20damage%20may%20be%20a%20concern%20if%20you%20live%20near%20a%20body%20of%20water%20or%20have%20a%20dog%20who%20likes%20to%20roll%20in%20the%20mud%20or%20expect%20your%20dog%20to%20spend%20time%20outside%20in%20the%20rain.%20If%20this%20sounds%20like%20your%20situation%2C%20look%20for%20a%20tracker%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iec.ch%2Fip-ratings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20waterproof%20rating%20of%20IPX7%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20higher%2C%20which%20indicates%20it%20can%20handle%20being%20submerged%20for%2030%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%20and%20comfort%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Adding%20a%20large%2C%20heavy%20object%20to%20the%20collar%20around%20a%20dog's%20neck%20can%20create%20discomfort.%20Ideally%2C%20a%20tracker%20should%20weigh%20no%20more%20than%20a%20couple%20of%20ounces.%20Owners%20with%20small%20breeds%20or%20those%20who%20want%20to%20track%20their%20cat%20should%20look%20for%20the%20manufacturer's%20weight%20recommendations%20to%20ensure%20the%20tracker%20is%20designed%20for%20smaller%20pets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20life%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Most%20trackers%20have%20integrated%20rechargeable%20batteries.%20Some%20recharge%20with%20their%20own%20unique%20cords%20that%20come%20in%20the%20box%2C%20while%20others%20use%20a%20standardized%20cord%2C%20such%20as%20USB-C.%20Trackers%20with%20longer%20battery%20life%20are%20more%20convenient.%20If%20your%20dog%20isn't%20found%20right%20away%20because%20they%20wandered%20into%20an%20area%20without%20a%20cellular%20signal%2C%20a%20longer%20battery%20life%20will%20help%20ensure%20you%20receive%20an%20updated%20location%20when%20connectivity%20is%20reestablished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ee2dd49-2442-47d0-89a2-7270b34ad756%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%2010%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20over%20several%20weeks%2C%20rating%20them%20across%20seven%20evaluation%20points.%20When%20my%20active%20sport%20breed%20dog%20wasn't%20wearing%20the%20trackers%2C%20I%20drove%20around%20with%20them%20to%20see%20just%20how%20fast%20and%20accurately%20they%20could%20track%20a%20runaway%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20setup%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20trackers%20can%20be%20a%20pain%20to%20attach%20to%20collars%20and%20their%20respective%20apps%20can%20come%20with%20a%20learning%20curve.%20I%20tracked%20how%20long%20it%20took%20to%20set%20up%20each%20collar%2C%20including%20attaching%20the%20tracking%20device%20and%20setting%20up%20the%20app.%20I%20noted%20how%20many%20times%20I%20needed%20to%20Google%20a%20question%20that%20wasn't%20answered%20in%20the%20instruction%20manual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20considered%20how%20much%20maintenance%20each%20tracker%20required%2C%20including%20cleaning%20and%20recharging%2C%20and%20how%20simple%20the%20app%20was%20to%20use%20long-term.%20I%20also%20noted%20whether%20the%20tracker%20got%20in%20the%20way%20of%20a%20resting%20dog%20or%20needed%20to%20be%20removed%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccuracy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20test%20accuracy%2C%20I%20played%20a%20literal%20game%20of%20hide-and-seek%20with%20another%20person.%20One%20person%20took%20the%20trackers%20and%20hid%20them%20around%20a%20park%20while%20the%20other%20used%20the%20app%20to%20attempt%20to%20locate%20the%20collar.%20As%20we%20searched%2C%20we%20considered%20things%20like%20how%20detailed%20the%20map%20was%20and%20how%20close%20it%20was%20to%20the%20actual%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlert%20speed%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20drove%20around%20with%20the%20trackers%20for%20several%20days%2C%20noting%20which%20ones%20were%20first%20to%20alert%20that%20the%20geofence%20had%20been%20breached%20along%20with%20any%20inconsistencies%20and%20missed%20alerts.%20Some%20of%20the%20trackers%20took%2030%20minutes%20to%20send%20a%20notification%2C%20while%20others%20wouldn't%20send%20a%20notification%20if%20my%20smartphone%20was%20with%20the%20tracker%2C%20assuming%20that%20I%20was%20still%20with%20my%20dog%20on%20a%20walk.%20Testing%20the%20geofence%20alerts%20by%20driving%20around%20with%20them%20allowed%20me%20to%20test%20them%20multiple%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReliability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20conducted%20most%20of%20the%20tests%20in%20a%20rural%20area%20and%20noted%20any%20outages%2C%20glitches%2C%20or%20dead%20zones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%20and%20waterproofing%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20testing%2C%20I%20examined%20the%20trackers%20for%20damage.%20Then%20I%20simulated%20scratching%20by%20scraping%20each%20one%20with%20a%20fork%2050%20times.%20I%20also%20put%20each%20tracker%20attached%20to%20a%20collar%20on%20a%20plush%20toy%20and%20scratched%20at%20it%20with%20sticks%20multiple%20times%20to%20see%20if%20the%20tracker%20detached%20from%20the%20collar%20itself.%20I%20dropped%20the%20trackers%20on%20a%20hard%20surface%20from%20waist%20height%20five%20times.%20Finally%2C%20if%20waterproofing%20was%20advertised%2C%20I%20placed%20the%20tracker%20under%20the%20shower%20for%20five%20minutes.%20If%20submersion%20was%20advertised%2C%20I%20placed%20it%20in%20a%20bowl%20of%20water%20for%2010%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdditional%20features%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20main%20test%20points%2C%20I%20considered%20each%20tracker's%20additional%20features%2C%20such%20as%20ringtones%20and%20lights%20for%20finding%20a%20lost%20dog%20in%20the%20dark.%20I%20also%20factored%20in%20the%20tracker's%20size%2C%20price%2C%20and%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f06f0b2-dfd6-48f9-952f-97d7164282b8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDog%20GPS%20tracker%20FAQs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20can%20help%20pet%20owners%20locate%20a%20lost%20pet%20and%20monitor%20their%20activity%20levels.%20But%20whether%20a%20tracker%20is%20worth%20the%20subscription%20costs%20depends%20on%20the%20dog's%20tendencies%20and%20the%20owner's%20lifestyle.%20GPS%20trackers%20can%20be%20highly%20valuable%20for%20dogs%20who%20are%20a%20flight%20risk%2C%20such%20as%20those%20who%20have%20a%20tendency%20to%20escape%20a%20backyard%20fence%20or%20dogs%20who%20cannot%20resist%20the%20temptation%20to%20chase%20a%20wild%20animal.%20A%20tracker%20can%20be%20a%20valuable%20aid%20if%20you%20have%20an%20overweight%20pet%20and%20want%20to%20increase%20your%20activity%20levels.%20Lifestyle%20can%20also%20come%20into%20play.%20For%20example%2C%20trackers%20can%20be%20helpful%20for%20hiking%20with%20your%20dog%20off-leash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20GPS%20tracker%20for%20a%20pet%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20pet%20GPS%20tracker%20is%20one%20that%20delivers%20fast%2C%20accurate%20location%20tracking%2C%20along%20with%20other%20features%20that%20match%20the%20pet%20and%20owner's%20lifestyle.%20For%20most%20dogs%2C%20we%20recommend%20the%20Fi%20Series%203%20for%20its%20speed%2C%20accuracy%2C%20and%20comfortable%20design.%20The%20Whistle%20Go%20Explore%202%20tracks%20more%20activity%20and%20the%20distance%20tracking%20is%20preferable%20to%20Fi's%20step%20count.%20Tractive%20sits%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20point%20yet%20still%20has%20accurate%20tracking%20with%20an%20exceptionally%20detailed%20map.%20The%20Cube%20GPS%20is%20a%20reliable%20tracker%20and%20provides%20the%20most%20privacy%20since%20it%20lacks%20social%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20dog%20GPS%20tracker%20doesn't%20require%20a%20subscription%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGPS%20trackers%20rely%20on%20cellphone%20signals%2C%20which%20means%20a%20subscription%20is%20required.%20Bluetooth%20trackers%20do%20not%20require%20a%20subscription.%20However%2C%20they%20only%20work%20when%20less%20than%20100%20feet%20away%20from%20a%20Bluetooth%20device%2C%20which%20means%20they%20are%20far%20less%20reliable%20than%20cellular-based%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20far%20do%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20work%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGPS%20trackers%20that%20use%20a%20cell%20signal%20will%20work%20anywhere%20a%20signal%20is%20available.%20Note%20that%20some%20trackers%20are%20only%20designed%20to%20work%20in%20the%20US%20and%20may%20not%20internationally.%20If%20a%20pet%20wanders%20into%20an%20area%20that%20lacks%20cell%20coverage%2C%20most%20trackers%20will%20display%20the%20pet's%20last%20known%20location.%20Accuracy%20for%20these%20trackers%20varies%20based%20on%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20the%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20we%20recommend%20were%20accurate%20down%20to%20just%20a%20few%20feet%2C%20while%20others%20I%20tested%20showed%20my%20dog%20across%20the%20road%20from%20where%20he%20actually%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20safe%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20dogs%20can%20safely%20wear%20a%20GPS%20tracker.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8465301%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%20conducted%20in%20Austria%20in%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20the%20radio%20frequency%20transmitted%20by%20GPS%20collars%20was%20unlikely%20to%20cause%20adverse%20health%20effects.%20Some%20types%20of%20dogs%2C%20however%2C%20should%20avoid%20using%20GPS%20trackers.%20Pritchard%20says%20owners%20should%20seek%20veterinary%20advice%20before%20adding%20weight%20to%20a%20collar%20on%20any%20dog%20with%20diagnosed%20neck%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20degenerative%20disk%20disease.%20Multi-dog%20households%20where%20the%20dogs%20are%20regularly%20nipping%20at%20each%20other's%20necks%20may%20also%20want%20to%20avoid%20the%20trackers%20for%20chewing%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrackers%20also%20come%20with%20inherent%20privacy%20risks.%20These%20risks%20may%20be%20higher%20for%20certain%20individuals%20who%20are%20experiencing%20domestic%20violence%20situations%20or%20are%20concerned%20about%20policing.%20Weiner%20says%20the%20problem%20is%20the%20tracker%20itself%2C%20but%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20rules%20surrounding%20what%20happens%20to%20your%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-gps-pet-trackers%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744406545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f980393fe8d3928362ea9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-gps-pet-trackers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20dog%20GPS%20trackers%20can%20help%20you%20locate%20a%20missing%20pet%20and%20track%20their%20activity.%20Our%20top%20picks%20are%20from%20Fi%2C%20Whistle%2C%20Tractive%2C%20and%20Cube.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Hillary%20Grigonis%2CSorin%20McKnight)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-gps-pet-trackers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22