ps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20self-described%20%26quot%3Btheater%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wanted%20to%20get%20the%20story%20out%2C%20so%20she%20started%20recording%20and%20sharing%20videos%20about%20the%20floods.%20She%20says%20her%20efforts%20raised%202%20million%20Nigerian%20Naira%20(roughly%20%245%2C000%20in%202020%20dollars)%20to%20help%20rebuild%20two%20local%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20youth%20NGO%20she%20founded%2C%20called%20Preserve%20Our%20Roots.%20They%20produced%20a%20documentary%20about%20the%20climate%20crisis%20in%20Africa%20in%202023%2C%20which%20you%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQTVbcUS3MLs%26ab_channel%3DPreserveOurRoots%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatch%20on%20Youtube%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20reaction%20to%20her%20documentary%20made%20her%20want%20to%20help%20Nigerians%20connect%20more%20with%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20came%20to%20us%20and%20was%20like%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20it%20in%20my%20community.%20I%20don't%20see%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20Nwuneli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20group%20decided%20to%20bring%20the%20nature%20home%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0starting%20with%20a%20small%20park%20that%20wouldn't%20require%20a%20lengthy%20government%20approval%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20site%20in%20Ikota%2C%20Nigeria%2C%20Nwuneli%20worked%20with%20local%20artisans%20to%20procure%20reclaimed%20metal%20and%20wood%2C%20as%20well%20as%20tires%20that%20were%20laying%20around%20the%20area%2C%20to%20build%20a%20slide%2C%20swings%2C%20and%20climbing%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22teen%20girl%20with%20long%20microbraids%20poses%20smiling%20with%20group%20of%20uniformed%20schoolchildren%20in%20front%20of%20a%20yellow%20swingset%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f860e1c6ad288d147ddec2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENwuneli%20poses%20with%20students%20at%20the%20newly%20opened%20park.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Okosun%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20area%2C%20which%20Nwuneli%20described%20as%20a%20slum%2C%20is%20flood-prone.%20Indeed%2C%20many%20of%20the%20surrounding%20houses%20are%20built%20on%20stilts%2C%20she%20said.%20So%2C%20with%20the%20help%20of%20donations%20and%20volunteers%2C%20Nwuneli's%20NGO%20planted%20flood-resistant%20trees%20around%20the%20playground%20%E2%80%94%20among%20300%20trees%20she%20says%20they%20planted%20across%20the%20wider%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20first%20homed%20in%20on%20this%20dump%20site%20in%20November.%20On%20March%201%2C%20they%20opened%20the%20park%20for%20schoolchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20when%20the%20children%20were%20like%2C%20'now%20something%20we%20can%20actually%20call%20beautiful.'%20It%20kind%20of%20broke%20my%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20Nwuneli%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20eyes%2C%20though%2C%20this%20is%20just%20a%20pilot%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294e36a2a-1564-4a05-9675-cae95faf59c1%5C%22%3EA%20Central%20Park%20for%20Lagos%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Earth%20Prize%20funding%2C%20Nwuneli%20is%20planning%20three%20more%20parks.%20They%20won't%20be%20playgrounds%20like%20the%20one%20that%20opened%20in%20March%2C%20she%20says%2C%20but%20multi-functional%20community%20hubs%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Furban-farming-gardening-carbon-footpring-study-produce-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egardens%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20greenhouses%2C%20and%20waste%20collection%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20aiming%20to%20convert%20a%20large%20landfill%20in%20Lagos%2C%20pending%20government%20approval.%20For%20the%20other%20two%20parks%2C%20she's%20targeting%20the%20neighboring%20Nigerian%20states%20of%20Ogun%20and%20Oyo%2C%20which%20are%20also%20experiencing%20floods%20and%20droughts%20that%20will%20likely%20get%20worse%