%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20cool%20car%20are%20stuck%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcybertruck-drivers-face-damages-repairs-mardi-gras-parade-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20some%20sort%20of%20political%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20wanted%20to%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20kids%2C%20it's%20a%20different%20story.%20Kids%20%3Cem%3Elove%3C%2Fem%3E%20Cybertrucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20sense.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20kids%20love%20trucks!%20For%20a%20preschooler%2C%20passing%20by%20an%20active%20construction%20site%20is%20like%20being%20a%20VIP%20at%20Coachella.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cybertruck%20is%20big%2C%20it's%20distinctive.%20It's%20rare.%20Seeing%20one%20on%20the%20road%20or%20even%20in%20a%20parking%20lot%20is%20a%20head-turner.%20It%20looks%20like%20it%20was%20made%20in%20Minecraft%20or%20out%20of%20Legos.%20It's%20absolutely%20aesthetically%20thrilling%20for%20a%20demographic%20that%20can't%20yet%20tie%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%206-year-old%20loves%20Teslas%20but%20has%20no%20idea%20who%20Musk%20is%2C%20and%20that's%20intentional%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mandy%20Shobar%2C%20a%20parent%20of%20two%20boys%20in%20Castro%20Valley%2C%20California.%20Shobar%20herself%20is%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20Telsa's%20CEO%20for%20reasons%20that%20would%20make%20sense%20to%20other%20adults%20but%20not%20a%20kindergartener.%20Her%20older%20son%2C%209%2C%20is%20less%20excited%20about%20the%20Cybertruck.%20%26quot%3BHe%20says%20they%20look%20'glitchy.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20Business%20Insider%20office%2C%20parents%20also%20noted%20their%20kids%20were%20obsessed%20with%20Cybertrucks.%20My%20boss's%20first%20grader%20recently%20brought%20home%20a%20piece%20of%20art%20from%20school%20dedicated%20to%20the%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20kid's%20drawing%20of%20a%20cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22htt