cause%20of%20his%20political%20opinions%20and%20role%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20really%20something%20that%20is%20easily%20explained%20to%20a%20small%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20too%20many%20years%20ago%20that%20Musk%20seemed%20like%20an%20unproblematic%20aspirational%20STEM%20figure%20for%20young%20kids.%20But%20with%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%202024%20election%20and%20now%20DOGE%2C%20the%20public's%20perception%20of%20Musk%20has%20changed.%20According%20to%20Nate%20Silver's%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.natesilver.net%2Fp%2Felon-musk-polls-popularity-nate-silver-bulletin%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Silver%20Bulletin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Musk's%20favorability%20polling%20switched%20from%20positive%20to%20negative%20last%20summer%2C%20and%20he's%20now%20less%20popular%20than%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20with%2053.5%25%20%26quot%3Bunfavorable%26quot%3B%20ratings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETom%20Cook%20(no%20relation%20to%20Tim)%20isn't%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelsa%3C%2Fa%3E%20hater%20%E2%80%94%20he%20previously%20owned%20a%20Model%203.%20He%20thinks%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20however%2C%20is%20aesthetically%20unpleasing.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20technical%20aspects%20of%20it%20that%20are%20good%20(electrical%20components%20where%20Tesla%20does%20good%20engineering)%2C%20but%20the%20nexus%20of%20cost%2Fpracticality%2Flooks%2Fassociation%20with%20%5BMusk%5D%20make%20it%20just%20impossible%20to%20ever%20take%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20was%20surprised%20when%20his%203-year-old%20daughter%20made%20a%20piece%20of%20Cybertruck%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kids's%20art%20drawing%20of%20Cybertruck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f942e63fe8d3928362d9d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%203-year-old's%20collage%20work%20of%20a%20Cybertruck%3Cp%3ETom%20Cook%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20exists%20a%20world%20of%20Cybertruck%20paraphrenia%20for%20kids.%20Mattel's%20Hot%20Wheels%20makes%20a%20classic%20pocket-sized%20Cybertruck%20(my%20kids%20have%20one)%20and%20a%20larger%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Df7c0d6ec2a69260488ce66b17b955d8e92815cdf9b5e440735c71d310ad0da93%26postID%3D67f92a6cb154b4859e6f4308%26postSlug%3Dtesla-cybertruck-kids-love-elon-musk-2025-4%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FCybertruck-Diecast-Vehicles-Collection-CT3601S%252Fdp%252FB0DFGSQG9L%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edie-cast%20light-up%20Cybertruck%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20about%20%2420.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Amazon%20and%20other%20online%20stores%2C%20you%20can%20find%20a%20variety%20of%20other%20remote-controlled%20Cybertruck-shaped%20toys%20from%20various%20no-name%20brands.%20(It%20is%20unclear%20if%20some%20of%20these%20actually%20have%20licensing%20deals%20with%20Tesla%20as%20Mattel%20does.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20sells%20a%20%241%2C500%20battery-operated%20ride-on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop.tesla.com%2Fproduct%2Fcybertruck-for-kids%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECybertruck%20for%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20similar%20to%20Power%20Wheels.%20It%20can%20fit%20two%20kids%2C%20suggested%20age%20range%20of%206%20to%2012.%20Telsa%20also%20makes%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop.tesla.com%2Fproduct%2Fcyberquad-for-kids%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECyberquad%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20for%20kids%20ages%209%20to%2012%2C%20which%20is%20an%20ATV-style%20ride-on%20toy%2C%20selling%20for%20%241%2C650.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22739%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kid%20riding%20an%20atv%20on%20grass%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f94931c6ad288d147df1c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22660%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20sells%20the%20Cyberquad%20ride-on%20toy%20for%20kids.%3Cp%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fshop.tesla.com%2Fproduct%2Fcyberquad-for-kids%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20even%20a%20world%20of%20media%20about%20Cybertrucks%20for%20kids.%20One%20person%20told%20me%20her%205-year-old%20truck-loving%20kid%20has%20discovered%20a%20song%20on%20YouTube%20Kids%20he%20plays%20on%20repeat.%20(I%20dare%20anyone%20to%20try%20to%20not%20tap%20your%20toes%20to%20this%20banger.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FdZrneeZJOkg%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22CyberTruck%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20non-fiction%20books%20for%20kids%20about%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20not%20unlike%20the%20one%20on%20Telsa%20my%20son%20once%20brought%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20picture%20book%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D0a6a8731688a033fb3e4d44d8fdee2144f4c4805fc5c01ad8184c64874f77e6b%26postID%3D67f92a6cb154b4859e6f4308%26postSlug%3Dtesla-cybertruck-kids-love-elon-musk-2025-4%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FUgly-Truckling-Story-My-Cybertruck-ebook%252Fdp%252FB0CPCNMDXY%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Ugly%20Truckling%3A%20The%20Story%20of%20My%20Cybertruck.%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20The%20Amazon%20summary%20reads%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EWhen%20a%20dad%20brings%20home%20a%20Cybertruck%2C%20his%20daughter%20is%20less%20than%20impressed.%20With%20its%20unconventional%20and%20futuristic%20appearance%2C%20the%20truck%20seems%20like%20an%20ugly%20duckling%20in%20a%20world%20of%20familiar%20cars.%20But%20as%20the%20little%20girl%20begins%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20Cybertruck's%20capabilities%20and%20its%20potential%20to%20help%20the%20world%2C%20she%20begins%20to%20see%20it%20in%20a%20whole%20new%20light.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221189%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22book%20jacket%20The%20ugly%20truckling%2C%20a%20kid%20in%20front%20of%20a%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f94dadc6ad288d147df314%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ugly%20Truckling%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20picture%20book%20about%20a%20girl%20who%20learns%20to%20accept%20her%20father's%20new%20car.%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20parents%20who%20find%20the%20Cybertruck%20to%20be%20a%20totem%20of%20something%20they%20disagree%20with%20politically%2C%20it%20may%20be%20slightly%20jarring%20to%20see%20their%20kids%20squeal%20with%20glee%20when%20they%20see%20one%20cruising%20down%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20things%20that%20kids%20love%20that%20can%20make%20parents%20cringe%3A%20room-temperature%20apple%20juice%2C%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Shark%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20idea%20that%20being%20asked%20to%20put%20on%20shoes%20and%20coat%20in%20a%20timely%20manner%20is%20an%20affront%20to%20human%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20parents%20I%20heard%20from%20who%20don't%20always%20share%20the%20same%20opinions%20about%20the%20Cybertruck%20put%20too%20much%20worry%20into%20it.%20To%20them%2C%20it%20was%20an%20amusing%20passing%20phase%20that%20reminded%20them%20of%20the%20vast%20gulf%20between%20how%20a%20child%20sees%20the%20world%20and%20how%20we%20see%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%