20a%20blind%20trust%2C%20as%20some%20ethics-minded%20lawmakers%20advocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20many%20successful%20years%20of%20running%20my%20own%20business%2C%20I%20ran%20for%20Congress%20to%20bring%20that%20mindset%20to%20Washington.%20Now%20that%20I'm%20proudly%20serving%20the%20people%20of%20Northwest%20Georgia%2C%20I%20have%20signed%20a%20fiduciary%20agreement%20to%20allow%20my%20financial%20advisor%20to%20control%20my%20investments%2C%26quot%3B%20Greene%20said.%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20my%20investments%20are%20reported%20with%20full%20transparency.%20I%20refuse%20to%20hide%20my%20stock%20trades%20in%20a%20blind%20trust%20like%20many%20others%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sen.%20Bernie%20Moreno%20of%20Ohio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f95ac1a466d2b74ab2f996%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESen.%20Bernie%20Moreno%20of%20Ohio%20says%20he%20didn't%20take%20his%20own%20financial%20advice%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20buy%20stocks.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20episode%20has%20once%20again%20brought%20the%20issue%20of%20stock%20trading%20in%20Congress%20to%20the%20fore.%20The%20trades%20made%20by%20former%20House%20Speaker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnancy-pelosi-stock-trades-congress-investments-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENancy%20Pelosi's%20husband%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20long%20been%20a%20source%20of%20controversy%2C%20and%20for%20years%2C%20lawmakers%20in%20both%20parties%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20ban%20the%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrankly%2C%20I%20don't%20care%20if%20Democrats%20did%20it%2C%20I%20don't%20care%20if%20Republicans%20did%20it%2C%20we're%20not%20here%20to%20feed%20at%20the%20trough%2C%26quot%3B%20Ocasio-Cortez%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20either%20an%20appearance%2