s%20repeatedly%20undermine%20U.S.%20national%20security%20and%20betray%20American%20values%2C%26quot%3B%20Wynn-Williams%20said%20in%20her%20opening%20remarks%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fmeta-whistleblower-testimony-senate-judiciary-subcommittee%2F%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWynn-Williams%20alleges%20that%20Meta%20built%20custom%20censorship%20tools%20for%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20enabling%20extensive%20control%20over%20content%20moderation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESen%20Hawley%20opened%20the%20hearing%20by%20saying%20that%20Meta%20had%20%26quot%3Bstopped%20at%20absolutely%20nothing%20to%20prevent%26quot%3B%20Wednesday's%20testimony%20by%20Ms%20Wynn-Williams.%20He%20also%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20it%20that%20Facebook%20is%20so%20desperate%20to%20prevent%20this%20witness%20from%20telling%20what%20she%20knows%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20greatest%20trick%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20ever%20pulled%20was%20wrapping%20the%20American%20flag%20around%20himself%20and%20calling%20himself%20a%20patriot%20and%20saying%20he%20didn't%20offer%20services%20in%20China%2C%20while%20he%20spent%20the%20last%20decade%20building%20an%20%2418%20billion%20business%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20disputes%20these%20claims%2C%20stating%20that%20Wynn-Williams'%20testimony%20is%20%26quot%3Bdivorced%20from%20reality%20and%20riddled%20with%20false%20claims%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20Wynn-Williams%20maintains%20that%20Meta's%20actions%20were%20deliberate%2C%20citing%20the%20company's%20interest%20in%20expanding%20its%20business%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20company's%20spokesperson%20Ryan%20Daniels%20said%20that%20although%20Meta's%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20been%20public%20about%20the%20company's%20interest%20in%20offering%20its%20services%20in%20China%2C%20%26quot%3B%5BT%5Dhe%20fact%20is%20this%3A%20we%20do%20not%20operate%20our%20services%20in%20China%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWynn%20Williams%20also%20said%20that%20Meta%20worked%20%26quot%3Bhand%20in%20glove%26quot%3B%20with%20Beijing%20to%20create%20censorship%20tools%20to%20silence%20critics%20of%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWynn-Williams%20claims%20that%20Meta%20threatened%20her%20with%20%2450%2C000%20in%20punitive%20damages%20for%20speaking%20out%2C%20even%20if%20her%20statements%20are%20true.%20Meta%20clarifies%20that%20this%20amount%20is%20for%20each%20material%20violation%20of%20her%20separation%20agreement%2C%20not%20for%20testifying%20before%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20testimony%2C%20Wynn-Williams%20also%20alleged%20that%20Meta's%20artificial%20intelligence%20model%2C%20Llama%2C%20was%20used%20to%20help%20Chinese%20AI%20company%20DeepSeek.%20This%20claim%20has%20raised%20further%20questions%20about%20Meta's%20relationships%20with%20Chinese%20companies%20and%20its%20commitment%20to%20protecting%20user%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20last%20year%20on%20Llama%2C%20Meta%20spokesperson%20Andy%20Stone%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20alleged%20role%20of%20a%20single%20and%20outdated%20version%20of%20an%20American%20open-source%20model%20is%20irrelevant%20when%20we%20know%20China%20is%20already%20investing%20over%201T%20to%20surpass%20the%20US%20technologically%2C%20and%20Chinese%20tech%20companies%20are%20releasing%20their%20own%20open%20AI%20models%20as%20fast%2C%20or%20faster%2C%20than%20US%20ones.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20against%20Meta%20come%20amid%20heightened%20tensions%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20over%20national%20security%2C%20economic%20interests%2C%20and%20technological%20advancements.%20The%20Trump%20administration%20has%20increased%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20goods%20and%20is%20pursuing%20the%20sale%20of%20TikTok%20to%20an%20American%20buyer.%20The%20House%20of%20Representatives%20has%20also%20established%20a%20th