%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20my%20divorce%20was%20finalized.%20I%20didn't%20know%20this%20was%20the%20case.%20I've%20had%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20last%20name%20on%20the%20paperwork%20for%20decades%20despite%20not%20being%20together%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20to%20go%20to%20multiple%20agencies%2C%20each%20with%20their%20own%20costs%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20the%20request%20and%20finalize%20things.%20I%20would%20need%20to%20get%20copies%20of%20divorce%20paperwork%20from%20a%20clerk%2C%20file%20a%20form%20requesting%20the%20change%2C%20and%20pay%20between%20%24150%20to%20%24435%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20state%20it's%20being%20filed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20things%20are%20finalized%2C%20I%20will%20also%20have%20to%20change%20all%20of%20my%20IDs.%20There%20is%20a%20cost%20to%20getting%20a%20new%20license%20and%20passport%2C%20for%20example.%20And%20there's%20the%20added%20nonmonetary%20cost%20of%20time%20because%20it's%20not%20super%20straightforward%20to%20get%20all%20the%20paperwork%20needed%20for%20each%20of%20these%20steps.%20Ultimately%2C%20name%20changes%20are%20not%20the%20quickest%20or%20easiest%20process%20for%20someone%20to%20do%2C%20yet%20it%20was%20so%20easy%20for%20them%20to%20make%20the%20change%20when%20I%20got%20married%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20haven't%20taken%20the%20steps%20to%20legally%20change%20my%20name%20again%2C%20I've%20decided%20to%20go%20by%20my%20original%20name.%20But%20not%20everyone%20respects%20that.%20My%20mother%20has%20insisted%20that%20she%20list%20me%20by%20my%20formerly%20married%20name%20instead%20of%20my%20chosen%20one%20in%20family%20obits%2C%20for%20example%2C%20saying%20that%20this%20was%20about%20%26quot%3Blegality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20come%20to%20learn%20how%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20a%20name%20change%20can%20be%20complex.%20With%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F119th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F22%5C%22%20target%3D%