butes%20the%20increase%20in%20fatalities%20to%20climate%20change%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20villagers%2C%20despite%20issuing%20weather%20warnings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22MANOJ%20CHAURASIA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpatna%2Fstorm-lightning-toll-increases-to-80-in-state%2Farticleshow%2F120212009.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%206%2C000%20Living%20Immigrants%20Listed%20Dead%20In%20The%20US%20To%20Force%20Self-Deportation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20has%20taken%20a%20drastic%20step%20by%20classifying%20over%206%2C000%20living%20immigrants%20as%20dead%2C%20effectively%20cancelling%20their%20social%20security%20numbers%20and%20rendering%20them%20unable%20to%20work%20or%20access%20benefits.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20move%20aims%20to%20encourage%20these%20immigrants%20to%20%26quot%3Bself-deport%26quot%3B%20and%20return%20to%20their%20home%20countries.%20The%20immigrants%20targeted%20by%20this%20policy%20were%20allowed%20to%20enter%20and%20remain%20in%20the%20US%20temporarily%20under%20programs%20introduced%20by%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20lawfully%20obtained%20social%20security%20numbers%2C%20which%20are%20unique%20nine-digit%20numbers%20issued%20by%20the%20federal%20government%20to%20US%20citizens%2C%20permanent%20residents%2C%20and%20temporary%20working%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20numbers%20are%20used%20for%20various%20official%20purposes%2C%20including%20tracking%20earnings%20and%20contributions%20to%20the%20social%20security%20system.%20By%20stripping%20these%20immigrants%20of%20their%20social%20security%20numbers%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20is%20effectively%20cutting%20them%20off%20from%20many%20financial%20services%20and%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20use%20banks%20or%20other%20basic%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20is%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20immigrants%20who%20entered%20the%20US%20under%20Biden-era%20programs%2C%20including%20over%20900%2C000%20immigrants%20who%20used%20the%20CBP%20One%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20(DHS)%2C%20on%20Monday%2C%20revoked%20the%20legal%20status%20of%20immigrants%20who%20used%20the%20CBP%20One%20app%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20US%20for%20two%20years%20with%20work%20authorisation%20under%20presidential%20parole%20authority%20during%20the%20Biden%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20are%20now%20expected%20to%20self-deport.%20A%20federal%20judge%20has%20stopped%20the%20Trump%20administration%20from%20ordering%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Cubans%2C%20Haitians%2C%20Nicaraguans%2C%20and%20Venezuelans%20with%20temporary%20legal%20status%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkye%20Perryman%2C%20President%20and%20CEO%20of%20Democracy%20Forward%2C%20an%20advocacy%20group%20that%20has%20challenged%20various%20Trump%20administration%20efforts%20in%20court%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20president%20continues%20to%20engage%20in%20lawless%20behavior%2C%20violating%20the%20law%20and%20abusing%20our%20systems%20of%20checks%20and%20balances.%26quot%3B%20The%20group%20is%20likely%20to%20sue%20over%20the%20social%20security%20numbers%20once%20more%20details%20become%20available%2C%20per%20the%20Associated%20Press%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20related%20development%2C%20DHS%20and%20the%20Treasury%20Department%20signed%20a%20deal%20allowing%20the%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%20(IRS)%20to%20share%20immigrants'%20tax%20data%20with%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20for%20deportation%20purposes.%20This%20agreement%20enables%20ICE%20to%20submit%20names%20and%20addresses%20of%20immigrants%20inside%20the%20US%20illegally%20to%20the%20IRS%20for%20cross-verification%20against%20tax%20records.%20The%20acting%20IRS%20commissioner%2C%20Melanie%20Krause%2C%20stepped%20down%20over%20this%20deal%2C%20which%20has%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20potential%20misuse%20of%20taxpayer%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration's%20efforts%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20immigrants%20have%20also%20faced%20legal%20challenges.%20A%20federal%20judge%20temporarily%20blocked%20a%20team%20led%20by%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20from%20accessing%20social%20security%20systems%20containing%20personal%20data%20on%20millions%20of%20Americans%2C%20calling%20their%20work%20a%20%26quot%3Bfishing%20expedition.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744383600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fhs7dgf6o_donald-trump_625x300_10_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-6000-living-immigrants-listed-dead-in-the-us-to-force-self-deportation-8142203%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Trump%20administration%20has%20taken%20a%20drastic%20step%20by%20classifying%20over%206%2C000%20living%20immigrants%20as%20deceased%2C%20effectively%20cancelling%20their%20social%20security%20numbers%20and%20rendering%20them%20unable%20to%20work%20or%20access%20benefits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fover-6000-living-immigrants-listed-dead-in-the-us-to-force-self-deportation-8142203%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australia's%20looming%20election%20brings%20housing%20crisis%20into%20focus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744383461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F9d05%2Flive%2F12f0fec0-1694-11f0-b1b3-7358f8d35a35.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcq5wlevy647o%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australia's%20housing%20crisis%20has%20hit%20its%20worst%20point%20