0communication%20tools%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20fly%20without%20being%20easily%20tracked.%20To%20avoid%20public%20tracking%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20the%20aircraft%20transporting%20Rana%20used%20a%20dummy%20call%20sign%2C%20making%20it%20invisible%20to%20live%20flight%20radars%20and%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%2C%20who%20was%20handcuffed%20and%20shackled%2C%20was%20escorted%20by%20a%20special%20NIA%20team%2C%20including%20an%20Inspector%20General%2C%20a%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General%2C%20and%20other%20intelligence%20officials.%20The%20flight%20was%20closely%20monitored%2C%20and%20the%20G550's%20real-time%20coordination%20features%20allowed%20the%20team%20to%20stay%20connected%20with%20authorities%20in%20India%20throughout%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20the%20G550%20won%20the%20Robert%20J%20Collier%20Trophy%20for%20its%20safety%20features%20and%20advanced%20technology.%C2%A0%20The%20cockpit%20uses%20the%20Honeywell%20PlaneView%20system%20and%20is%20built%20to%20handle%20encrypted%20communication%2C%20making%20the%20plane%20a%20secure%20flying%20base%20%E2%80%93%20far%20safer%20than%20a%20regular%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G550%20is%20also%20used%20in%20military%20roles%2C%20modified%20for%20surveillance%2C%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20and%20reconnaissance.%20Some%20models%2C%20like%20the%20EA-37B%2C%20are%20designed%20to%20disrupt%20enemy%20radar%20and%20communication%20networks.%C2%A0They%20can%20also%20be%20equipped%20with%20high-tech%20tools%20like%20missile%20warning%20systems%2C%20countermeasure%20dispensers%2C%20and%20secure%20radios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gulfstream%20G550%20is%20built%20for%20long-haul%20missions%20with%20impressive%20performance%20capabilities.%20It%20has%20a%20top%20speed%20of%20Mach%200.885%20and%20a%20maximum%20range%20of%2012%2C501%20km%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20fly%20non-stop%20for%20up%20to%2013%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPowe